    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv-team-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at Gradation 1 given Medium model influence and the availability of experimental confirmation testing. The CFD model is assessed as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is met at all five COU operating points with the predicted worst-case condition identified at 2 L/min / 2500 RPM. The credibility assessment supports the regulatory submission decision.",
